content:
[[module CSS]]

div#container-wrap {
    background-image: url(http://scp-ukrainian.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3Ain-memoriam-nazare/body_bg_black.png);
}

#header {
    background: url(http://scp-ukrainian.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3Ain-memoriam-nazare/White_Crow_100x100.png) 10px 40px no-repeat;
}

#header h2 span {
    color: transparent;  
    text-shadow: none;
}

#header h2 span::before {
    content: "乌克兰分部。为纪念NaZare。 ";
    color: #ffffff;
}

#footer a {
    color: #000000;
    background: transparent;
}

#side-bar .side-block {
    border: 1px solid #000000;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(128,128,128,1);
    background: #ffffff;
}

#top-bar ul li.sfhover a,
#top-bar ul li:hover a {
    color: #000000;
}

#top-bar ul li ul a,
#top-bar a:hover {
    color: #000000;
}

.side-block .menu-item > .image {
    filter: grayscale(100%);
    -webkit-filter: grayscale(100%);
}

#side-bar .heading {
    color: #000000;
    border-bottom: solid 1px #000000;
}

a {
    color: #000000;
}

.content-panel {
    background-color: #000000;
}

.content-panel .panel-body {
    background: #ffffff;
}

h1, #page-title {
    color: #000000;
}

.page-rate-widget-box .rate-points {
    background-color: #000000 !important;
    border: solid 1px #000000;
}

.page-rate-widget-box .rateup,
.page-rate-widget-box .ratedown {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-top: solid 1px #000000;
    border-bottom: solid 1px #000000;
}

.page-rate-widget-box .rateup a,
.page-rate-widget-box .ratedown a {
    color: #000000;
}

.page-rate-widget-box .rateup a:hover,
.page-rate-widget-box .ratedown a:hover {
    background: #000000;
    color: #ffffff;
}

.page-rate-widget-box .cancel {
    background-color: #000000;
    border: solid 1px #000000;
}

.page-rate-widget-box .cancel a {
    color: #ffffff;
}

.page-rate-widget-box .cancel a:hover {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #ffffff;
}

#footer {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
}

#search-top-box-input, #search-top-box input.empty,
#search-top-box-form input[type=submit] {
    transition: 0.2s linear;
}

#search-top-box-input, #search-top-box input.empty {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #ffffff;
    border-radius: 0;
    color: #fff;
}

#search-top-box-input:hover, #search-top-box-input:focus,
#search-top-box input.empty:hover, #search-top-box input.empty:focus {
    outline: 0;
    border: 1px solid #fff;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.8);
}

#search-top-box-form input[type=submit] {
    outline: 0;
    height: 1.65em;
    border: 1px solid #ffffff;
    border-radius: 0;
    color: #fff;
    background: #000000;

    position: relative;
    top: -1px;

    box-shadow: none;
}

#search-top-box-form input[type=submit]:hover,
#search-top-box-form input[type=submit]:focus {
    border: 1px solid #fff;
    border-radius: 0;
    background: #000000;
}

#search-top-box-form input[type=submit]:active {
    padding: 0 0.5em;
    border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    border-radius: 0;
    color: #fff;
    background: #000000;
}

 /* Mobile Media Queries */
@media (max-width: 767px) {
    #side-bar {
        background-color: #000000;
    }

    #top-bar .open-menu a {
        border: 0.2em solid #000000;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #000000;
    }


}

[[/module]]
[[iftags +版式]]

> 本版式由[[*user Dasgot]]基于[[*user Comrade Xander]]的概念，并在[[*user N_Nivis]]的帮助下开发，谨此纪念我们的朋友和同事[[*user NaZare]]，他为保卫乌克兰抵御俄罗斯入侵而牺牲。图像编辑自[*https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Crow_Digital_Logo_SVG.svg Crow Logo SVG]，来自[https://crow.com.tr/ CrowDigital]。

